<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL10">
<l>nāṭṭiṉāṉ teyva meṅkum nallatō raruḷtaṉ ṉālē</l>
<l>kāṭṭiṉāṉ tiruva raṅka muypavark kuyyum vaṇṇaṅ</l>
<l>kēṭṭirē nampi mīrkāḷ keruṭavā kaṉaṉu niṟkac</l>
<l>cēṭṭaitaṉ maṭiya kattuc celvampārt tirukkiṉ ṟīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He established gods everywhere. Out of [His] unique grace that is good,</l>
<l>He showed Śrīraṅgam [in such] a way that those [willing] to be saved are saved.</l>
<l>Did you hear, O superior people! While there is [the Lord] with Garuḍa for [His] vehicle,</l>
<l>You are seeking wealth in the lap of Jyeṣṭhā!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
